# Enable colored fonts in various of terminals (e.g. built-in terminal, terminator)

Go to ~/.bashrc, uncommnet the line force_color_prompt = yes

In terminaotor, right-click the background -> preferences -> general, to set font size to 12

# Establish Thunderbird at Startup and minimize

Go to "Startup Applications" (by search), add a new entry:
Name: thunderbird
Command: thunderbird

Go to thunderbird -> tools -> add-on -> extension panel
Find the webpage of "firetray" in a web browser, drag the green "download" button into the extension panel in thunderbird and install. 
Open the settings of "firetray", select "start application hidden to tray"
